# ==============================================================================
# CRYPTO-AI-BOT — MASTER .ENV (Prod-ready w/ Regime Detection, AI, Discord)
# ==============================================================================
# UTF-8 (no BOM). Replace YOUR_... placeholders. Keep comments; some scripts read them.
